  <div class="description">
    <h3 id="comment:description">
      Description
    </h3>
    <div class="searchable">
      <p>
I'm intending on applying for GSoC 2016 and the wiki mentions it would be nice if I've done some work in the area - so this is my attempt to do so.<br />
</p>
<p>
Summary speaks for itself. We should look at using a CBV for the flatpages view. I notice there is an extra internal view and I'll look into seeing if there's a nice way of integrating it into the CBV rather than just calling it from within it.<br />
</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
          

